I borrowed it from my
company's hangar.

92
00:07:23,776 --> 00:07:27,780
I was supposed to test drive it,
but do you know what this bike means?

93
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:35,079
- So what does \"Bahamood\" mean?
- \"From Bahamut.\"

94
00:07:35,246 --> 00:07:37,290
- B.D.: Why, Mr. Nakagawa.
- [GASPS]

95
00:07:37,457 --> 00:07:42,128
You know that the company frowns on
the borrowing of classified materials.

96
00:07:42,295 --> 00:07:43,963
I trust you'll come quietly.

97
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:47,258
