sending out goons with handguns?

98
00:07:47,425 --> 00:07:51,220
- Shinji! - Don't move! - These guys are GS!
- Shogo, Plan E! - Yeah, got it!

99
00:07:51,387 --> 00:07:53,073
- B.D.: Don't be stupid, Nakagawa!
- [MOTORCYCLE STARTS]

100
00:07:53,097 --> 00:07:55,099
Don't force our hand!

101
00:07:59,937 --> 00:08:01,063
[SHINJI SCREAMS IN PAIN]

102
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:04,317
- Damn! Go around back.
- Shinji!

103
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:08,237
