Shinji for this thing?

114
00:08:51,447 --> 00:08:54,742
- There's no way I'm not gonna make them pay.
- Coco: Cool it, hothead.

115
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:58,454
Getting all worked up and flying off the
handle's not gonna do anyone any good.

116
00:08:59,413 --> 00:09:01,999
