think they are, you'd better lay low.

119
00:09:12,009 --> 00:09:16,847
Yeah, dude. And if they want this thing, just
leave it somewhere and let them find it.

120
00:09:17,014 --> 00:09:19,850
Look, I've got an idea,
but I'll need your help.

121
00:09:20,017 --> 00:09:21,727
Radio: The target's name is Shogo Yahagi.

122
00:09:21,811 --> 00:09:24,397
