going on. I'll show you the bike.

202
00:14:12,726 --> 00:14:15,771
All right then. And I'll see
if I can find your friend.

203
00:14:15,938 --> 00:14:19,900
And by the way, I guess I forgot to say
that you can put the receiver down.

204
00:14:20,067 --> 00:14:22,528
Oh, I can, huh?
[EMBARRASSED CHUCKLE]

205
00:14:22,695 --> 00:14:25,447
Well then, can your video see this?

206
00:14:25,531 --> 00:14:28,158
- That's the bike, right there.
- Eve: Yes, I see it.

207
00:14:28,325 --> 00:14:30,286
Shogo: And no one else ever has.

208
00:14:30,452 --> 00:14:35,165
It'll do 200! And it even survived
a head-on collision with a Beemer.

209
00:14:35,332 --> 00:14:36,834
