212
00:14:42,673 --> 00:14:45,175
Actually, I don't know much
about motorcycles...

213
00:14:45,259 --> 00:14:47,553
but I've never seen
one this big before.

214
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:51,765
So what I was hoping was that I could bring
this bike into your station for safekeeping.

215
00:14:51,849 --> 00:14:54,435
