watch in the first place? Uhh! What a freak!

227
00:15:33,724 --> 00:15:36,894
Maybe he likes you,
and was going to confess it.

228
00:15:37,061 --> 00:15:39,146
- Shut up, dork.
- Mai: Shhh! This song's...

229
00:15:39,313 --> 00:15:41,774
been on top of the charts
for three weeks now!

230
00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:43,943
Let me listen!

231
00:15:46,278 --> 00:15:48,489
Lieutenant: All cars standing by.

232
00:15:48,656 --> 00:15:50,491
Mobile Unit Two to all units.

233
00:15:50,574 --> 00:15:53,994
Target is passing A-33.
Engage at the next intersection.

234
00:15:54,161 --> 00:15:56,080
Center-Forward, we confirm.

235
00:15:56,246 --> 00:15:58,332
This is Quarterback, confirm.

236
00:15:58,499 --> 00:16:00,376
Van Driver: Hold on.
Target's trying to pass.

237
00:16:00,751 --> 00:16:02,419
[HORN BLARES]

238
00:16:07,967 --> 00:16:10,803
- [RELIEVED SIGH]
- Hey! Watch where you're going, you moron!

239
00:16:10,970 --> 00:16:15,349
Say what?! Watch where I'm going?! You're
the one that ran into me, you jackass!

240
00:16:15,516 --> 00:16:19,979
- Oooh! Just get out of the way, you jerks!
I'm in a hurry! - Holy cow!

241
00:16:20,145 --> 00:16:22,564
- You're not injured, are you, buddy?
- Now! Take him down.

242
00:16:22,731 --> 00:16:24,709
- Hold on! Get on back here!
- Thought you could pull a fast one, did ya?

243
00:16:24,733 --> 00:16:27,027
Hey, fight fair! Owwww!

244
00:16:27,194 --> 00:16:30,823
- Stop him! Pull out the key!
- What the hell?!

245
00:16:38,122 --> 00:16:40,249
[EXCITING MUSIC]

246
00:16:40,332 --> 00:16:42,185
Lieutenant: I'm sorry, sir.
Target scored the touchdown.

247
00:16:42,209 --> 00:16:44,586
He's currently fleeing on Gaien,
towards Highway 246.

248
00:16:44,753 --> 00:16:47,756
Unit Two! You will force
the target onto Highway 3.

249
00:16:47,923 --> 00:16:49,758
We'll have a transport unit ready.

250
00:16:49,842 --> 00:16:52,011
You're ours, kid.

251
00:16:52,177 --> 00:16:54,179
[SQUEAL]

252
00:16:57,766 --> 00:16:59,119
Lieutenant: Target acquired.
We're in pursuit.

253
00:16:59,143 --> 00:17:01,729
Moving from the highway
toward the Yoyogi interchange.

254
00:17:01,895 --> 00:17:05,232
