- Soldier A: Understood.

256
00:17:12,197 --> 00:17:14,950
Oooooh SHIT!

257
00:17:23,876 --> 00:17:25,586
Where the hell are the other cars?

258
00:17:25,753 --> 00:17:27,921
They tricked me!

259
00:17:33,677 --> 00:17:36,096
