261
00:17:41,977 --> 00:17:43,371
Lieutenant: Just hold the ramp steady!

262
00:17:43,395 --> 00:17:45,397
Eyaaah!

263
00:17:46,273 --> 00:17:49,151
Desperate times call for-Yaaaaah!

264
00:17:52,112 --> 00:17:54,490
Lieutenant: Don't let him get away!
Initiate transformation!

265
00:17:54,656 --> 00:17:56,700
Corporal: Roger.

266
00:17:56,867 --> 00:17:58,952
Sergeant: Unit One,
transformation complete.

267
00:17:59,119 --> 00:18:01,705
Lieutenant: Understood.
Initiate capture.

268
00:18:01,872 --> 00:18:04,208
Sergeant: Target acquired!

269
00:18:04,374 --> 00:18:06,085
Wait! No! [SCREAMS]

270
00:18:06,251 --> 00:18:07,669
What the hell is that?!

271
00:18:07,836 --> 00:18:10,798
- Strikers, use the capture nets.
- Roger.

272
00:18:10,964 --> 00:18:13,550
I'm screwed!

273
00:18:13,634 --> 00:18:15,886
Geez! It is a robot!

274
00:18:18,013 --> 00:18:20,390
