275
00:18:20,557 --> 00:18:22,017
Truck Drivers: [SCREAM]

276
00:18:27,481 --> 00:18:31,610
[PANICKED CRIES]

277
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:40,285
Uh...? Huh...?

278
00:18:40,452 --> 00:18:43,455
