358
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:40,544
Awesome, girls, that's fabulous!
Now that's a wrap!

359
00:23:40,961 --> 00:23:44,673
- Yes, that's workin', people! Absolutely
fabulous! - [YUI LAUGHS NERVOUSLY]

360
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:49,219
- [SLOW CLAPPING BY ONE PERSON]
- Huh...?

361
00:23:51,888 --> 00:23:55,392
- Hey!
- Umm, I'm afraid something came up.

362
00:23:55,559 --> 00:23:59,187
- What?!
- I can't go out, not tonight.

363
00:23:59,354 --> 00:24:01,982
- Uh... - Sorry.
- Hey, wait up!

364
00:24:02,149 --> 00:24:03,442
Later, 'kay?

365
00:24:03,608 --> 00:24:07,654
- Hi... - So, see you at the Central
Hotel in an hour, right, Toots?

366
00:24:07,821 --> 00:24:09,281
Yui: Uh huh. I've got to change.

367
00:24:09,448 --> 00:24:10,991
That bastard!

368
00:24:11,616 --> 00:24:14,911
[SUSPENSEFUL BASS LINE]

369
00:24:25,255 --> 00:24:27,632
- Producer: So, Yui...
- Yes, sir.

370
00:24:27,799 --> 00:24:32,179
- Why don't you take a shower first?
- Umm... OK, sure.

371
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:38,143
That's the hotel that old
letch mentioned.

372
00:24:38,226 --> 00:24:40,854
The question... is what
room they're in.

373
00:24:41,104 --> 00:24:42,856
[DISTORTED CONVERSATION]

374
00:24:43,023 --> 00:24:44,858
Not there...

375
00:24:45,025 --> 00:24:47,819
Maybe up higher...

376
00:24:47,986 --> 00:24:50,405
[CRUNCH!]

377
00:24:53,700 --> 00:24:56,953
[DISTORTED] So whad'ya think of what
Princess Di wore last night, huh?

378
00:24:57,120 --> 00:25:01,416
[DISTORTED] Oh! Ahh!
Oh, Oh, right there! Oh!

379
00:25:17,557 --> 00:25:20,352
Producer: Oh yeah, Yui. Very hot.

380
00:25:24,648 --> 00:25:28,568
- [DISTORTED] Check out the hair, dude. - Dude,
do you like it? It's a Flock of Seagulls haircut.

381
00:25:28,735 --> 00:25:30,087
- Where are you?
- [DISTORTED] Everybody's gonna want one!

382
00:25:30,111 --> 00:25:32,322
[DISTORTED] I think I'd look
a lot better in that dress.

383
00:25:32,489 --> 00:25:35,468
- [DISTORTED] Man, will you shut up and
pass that shit?! - Call me your Queen!

384
00:25:35,492 --> 00:25:36,952
Producer: Oh, yeah.

385
00:25:47,170 --> 00:25:49,714
- [GASPS]
- [GRUNTS]

386
00:25:49,881 --> 00:25:53,593
- Yui: No. - Producer: Come on, baby.
- Yui: No, you're too rough.

387
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:55,696
Producer: But I wanna make you
the lead in my next production.

388
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,973
Got you, you bastard!

389
00:25:58,765 --> 00:26:00,684
[LOUD CRASH]

390
00:26:06,273 --> 00:26:07,983
[CONFUSED WHIMPERING]

391
00:26:08,149 --> 00:26:09,901
[TERRIFIED SCREAMS]

392
00:26:10,068 --> 00:26:12,279
No! No!

393
00:26:12,445 --> 00:26:15,448
[INCREDULOUS MOAN]

394
00:26:16,908 --> 00:26:18,577
Woah! Damn!

395
00:26:21,538 --> 00:26:25,417
[INCOHERENT GIBBERING]

396
00:26:32,632 --> 00:26:34,593
You big jerk!

397
00:26:36,553 --> 00:26:39,931
[LAUGHS HAPPILY]
I can't believe it.

398
00:26:40,098 --> 00:26:45,812
You said that it was weird, but who would
have thought it would do that! [LAUGHS]

399
00:26:45,895 --> 00:26:48,398
But what were you thinking?

400
00:26:51,735 --> 00:26:55,739
- What was that for? - What were you
thinking about with that... sleazeball?!

401
00:26:55,905 --> 00:26:59,159
That's not any of your
business, now is it?!

402
00:26:59,242 --> 00:27:02,120
And you! Let's talk about
what you did to me!

403
00:27:02,203 --> 00:27:05,707
What were you thinking?! Coming in
and grabbing me like you own me?!

404
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:10,045
You screwed it all up!
Just when... when I... I...

405
00:27:10,128 --> 00:27:13,673
was about to get the lead role.
That's all ruined now.

406
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:16,509
I can't believe you'd've slept
with him just to get a part!

407
00:27:16,676 --> 00:27:20,513
That's just between me and him!
Just... leave me alone!

408
00:27:33,693 --> 00:27:36,488
\"McDonald's Hamburgers\"

409
00:27:36,821 --> 00:27:40,408
Shogo: Yes, ma'am. That'll
be 2,350 yen, from 10,000.

410
00:27:40,492 --> 00:27:42,827
And your change is 7,650.

411
00:27:42,994 --> 00:27:44,663
Thanks, and have a McNice McDay.

412
00:27:44,829 --> 00:27:46,581
- Tomomi: Hey, Shogo!
- Huh?

413
00:27:46,748 --> 00:27:49,751
Hi. I've got a proposal for you.

414
00:27:52,545 --> 00:27:55,757
- A movie?
- Yeah, using that bike of yours.

415
00:27:55,924 --> 00:27:59,469
- I heard that it's rad. - She blabbed.
- Yup, us roomies talk.

416
00:27:59,636 --> 00:28:02,055
That motorcycle is way too
dangerous. Look, I-

417
00:28:02,222 --> 00:28:05,767
Yeah, but it looks so cool,
and there'd be no special effects.

418
00:28:05,934 --> 00:28:09,479
And you'd be the hero.
Opposite Yui, of course.

419
00:28:10,730 --> 00:28:13,650
And she's... OK with that, huh?

420
00:28:13,817 --> 00:28:15,777
Uh... Yeah...

421
00:28:16,986 --> 00:28:20,615
- I'll think about it.
