422
00:28:23,076 --> 00:28:24,994
Tomomi: I'm sorry about this.

423
00:28:25,161 --> 00:28:28,790
But we need to scout locations,
and you can cover a lot of ground quickly.

424
00:28:28,957 --> 00:28:31,084
And time is something we don't have.

425
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:37,048
It's weird. I didn't think
he'd say yes.

426
00:28:37,215 --> 00:28:38,967
Mai: Say yes to what?

427
00:28:39,134 --> 00:28:41,302
Nothing. I was just
thinking out loud.

428
00:28:41,469 --> 00:28:44,472
About Shogo, right?
You can't hide it from me!

429
00:28:44,639 --> 00:28:48,893
[GIGGLES AND SQUEALS]

430
00:28:53,815 --> 00:28:56,693
Oh oh... Smokey on
a bike. See him?

431
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:59,487
For a while. He's been
there following us.

432
00:29:03,283 --> 00:29:05,285
