699
00:49:45,190 --> 00:49:48,527
As a result, half of the
biospheres were abandoned.

700
00:49:48,694 --> 00:49:54,533
- Abandoned...
- Eve: 4,321,260 standard time units...

701
00:49:54,616 --> 00:49:58,286
500 years have passed
since 5930 was encoded.

702
00:49:58,370 --> 00:50:00,747
And now, the same error
is in progress.

703
00:50:00,831 --> 00:50:04,501
The same calamity that took
Biosphere Prime will claim this ship.

704
00:50:05,043 --> 00:50:07,462
Biosphere Prime? What is that?

705
00:50:07,796 --> 00:50:10,966
Biosphere Prime is Earth,
the human homeworld.

706
00:50:11,425 --> 00:50:16,722
- Hold on! Are you telling me that the
enemy are humans, just like us? - Correct.

707
00:50:16,888 --> 00:50:21,101
But if Bahamut's seventh-level program,
E.V.E., was online...

708
00:50:21,184 --> 00:50:23,061
it would be able to protect you.

709
00:50:23,145 --> 00:50:26,857
That is the purpose for which
it... I... was designed.

710
00:50:27,274 --> 00:50:30,193
However, this program
