750
00:52:52,878 --> 00:52:54,838
It's time to implement our plan.

751
00:53:02,929 --> 00:53:04,931
[SIGHS]

752
00:53:05,724 --> 00:53:10,687
~b~Eve: ~i~At morning's first light...

