773
00:54:12,707 --> 00:54:17,671
Asked for comment just now, government
officials stated that space-based warfare...

774
00:54:17,754 --> 00:54:20,423
now seems to be a grim reality.

775
00:54:20,507 --> 00:54:23,718
This station will keep you updated
as this story unfolds.

776
00:54:23,927 --> 00:54:31,927
Please forget...

