from discovering the truth?

835
00:58:29,714 --> 00:58:33,676
Yui: So, these people only think
their friends went somewhere else?

836
00:58:33,843 --> 00:58:39,307
Shogo: Uh-huh. It's all a sham.
Our world really is just a stage.

